{"tid":2338328,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"羅致光：本港貧窮情況有改善 稱政府扶貧不力目的只一個 — 「鬧(反)政府」","createTime":"2020-12-24T03:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T03:43:14.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39ac0b28c8ba9c99466ec0a134093bff11ed7a94","tid":2338328,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"羅致光：本港貧窮情況有改善 稱越扶越貧是謬誤<br />\n<br />\n政府發表去年香港貧窮情況報告，去年香港貧窮人口149.1萬，創下11年新高，貧窮率21.4%，勞工及福利局長羅致光指，有關數字理念上及事實上是錯誤，因為是假設政府並無任何政策介入，但實際上是有，認為用有關數字批評政府「越扶越貧」是謬誤，質疑外界引述數字目的只有一個，就是「鬧政府」。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光指，最精確的貧窮數字，是要計及政府介入政策後的數字，即約64萬人，貧窮率為9.2%，較前年的9.3%下跌0.1個百分點，認為政府雖然做得不夠，但情況是有改善。<br />\n<br />\n在明年的貧窮人口數據方面，羅致光預計，在政策介入前的貧窮數字很大機會上升，幅度亦不會小。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2372032&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MaCfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=18b35f65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372032</a>"},{"pid":"b74137be0044a9198d35327f92fe8b90cfbad69c","tid":2338328,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"今晚全港四區有活動 !!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[重post] 平安夜活動要人!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2337539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2337539</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b1bf29ced14d8954f406c9987f3603f2138618f","tid":2338328,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"少咗單程證抵港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89e3806d032ae0a072c47b1e038eff2b51833b3","tid":2338328,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0